{"id":"9612","user":{"id":"337130","nickname":"绝命徒神探","avatar_url":"https://static.codemao.cn/FpCHOmz10RBEcUMzkZhHX-o75Upr","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"title":"【萌新院讲堂】迟来了N天的Python教程：字符串","content":"<p><p><font size=\"7\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 【<font color=\"#ff0000\">···前言</font></font><font color=\"#ff0000\">·</font><span><font color=\"#ff0000\">···</font>】</span></p>\n<p><font size=\"4\">大家吼，我是绝命，今天我给大家带来一期Python教程，望大家喜欢。这是萌新向，Python大佬勿喷。首先，你要打开你自己Python IDLE。没下载的，用编程猫的下载按钮：</font></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FgxjF-eqE_bn4zCc2DToZ3gv3B1j\"><font size=\"4\"><br></font></p>\n<p><font size=\"4\">自己去下载，或者自己去Python官网下载，传送门：http：//www.python.org。然后界面就是介样。：</font></p> \n<img>\n<img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FqPLBvWnp-yI2Yuo6IT0h5CrE8-q\"> \n<img>\n<p><font size=\"7\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;【<font color=\"#00ffff\">···正文···</font>】</font></p>\n<p><font size=\"4\">Python小知识：什么是字符串</font></p>\n<p><font size=\"4\">字符串就是在引号内的东东，比如单引号、双引号、三引号。字符串也称文本，文本不同于数字。我举个栗子：</font></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FvIjA6W9vloWCm9z22w53I3_lGMZ\"><br></p>\n<p><font size=\"4\">在IDLE内输码：</font></p>\n<p><font size=\"4\">123+456</font></p>\n<p><font size=\"4\">然后敲下回车，就会这样：</font></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/Fk6MELYAk3rO2_FyvfwyBMZxOkN8\"><font size=\"4\"><br></font></p>\n<p>没错，你会看到是Python把它算出来了。然后你再输码：</p>\n<p>'123'+'456'（注意，编程里用的符号全都是英文的）然后敲下回车键就变成这样：</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/Fg796W4v1tItlQOLgI0BWR0vcFb3\"><br></p>\n<p>由此可见，加引号跟不加引号的差别是很大的，加引号表示把两个字符串放到一起。我再举个栗子：</p>\n<p>输码：</p>\n<p>myfriends=\"绝命徒\"</p>\n<p>yourfriends=\"神探\"</p>\n<p>ourfriends=myfriends+yourfriends</p>\n<p>print(ourfriends)</p>\n<p>结果：<img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FgFJ_KtgY_fpo1KeArCWplNG-Gfp\"></p>\n<p>现在清楚了吧。也许你会问：如果那个字符串很长，而且还有时换行怎么办？比如《逆战》这首歌，来，展示给你看：</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/Fkf_-AiCPq09tHdmO2bz6BjRIYm9\"><br></p>\n<p>“\\n”的意思就是换一行继续。就系介样。</p>\n<p><font size=\"7\">【<font color=\"#00ff00\">···尾声···</font>】</font></p>\n<p><font size=\"3\">今天我布置个作业：用Python搞一个要换行的字符串再评论区截图给我，要很长。</font></p>\n<p><br></p></p>","board_id":"2","board_name":"积木编程乐园","updated_at":1519732379,"created_at":1519557272,"n_views":254,"n_replies":32,"n_comments":0,"is_authorized":false,"is_featured":false,"is_hotted":false,"is_pinned":false,"tutorial_flag":0,"ask_help_flag":0}